@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fctara(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.80 + tmp + 0.61) - 0.23) / ((v1 + 0.79 / v1 + 0.84) + v2))
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.93 - v1 + 0.67)) - v0)
    v2 = wp.abs((tmp + wp.abs(tmp + 0.60)))
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.00 / v2 + 0.18)) + (v2 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.73)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.61 / v2 + 0.92)) * 0.74)
    data[tid] = v0
